## Uso BĂˇsico

```dart
// Verificar se estĂˇ logado (AuthFlowCubit registrado no getIt via init_auth)
final authCubit = getIt<AuthFlowCubit>();
final isLoggedIn = authCubit.state is AuthFlowAuthenticated;

// Login com Google
await authCubit.signInWithGoogle();

// Login com Apple (iOS only)
await authCubit.signInWithApple();

// Logout
await authCubit.signOut();

// Obter usuĂˇrio atual
if (authCubit.state is AuthFlowAuthenticated) {
  final user = (authCubit.state as AuthFlowAuthenticated).user;
  print(user.displayName);
}
```

## Estados (AuthFlowState)

| Estado | DescriĂ§ĂŁo |
|--------|-----------|
| `AuthFlowInitial` | Verificando estado inicial |
| `AuthFlowLoading` | Login em progresso |
| `AuthFlowUnauthenticated` | NĂŁo logado |
| `AuthFlowAuthenticated` | Logado (contĂ©m `AuthUser`) |
| `AuthFlowError` | Erro (contĂ©m `AuthException`) |

