## Providers Suportados

| Provider | Plataforma | ObrigatĂłrio |
|----------|------------|-------------|
| Google | Android, iOS | Sim |
| Apple | iOS | Sim* |
| Email | Todos | Opcional |

*Apple exige Sign in with Apple se o app oferece login social.

## ConfiguraĂ§ĂŁo Firebase

1. Firebase Console > Authentication > Sign-in method
2. Habilitar Google
3. Habilitar Apple (iOS)

### Android

SHA-1 fingerprint deve estar no Firebase Console.

### iOS

```xml
<!-- Info.plist -->
<key>CFBundleURLTypes</key>
<array>
  <dict>
    <key>CFBundleURLSchemes</key>
    <array>
      <string>com.googleusercontent.apps.YOUR_CLIENT_ID</string>
    </array>
  </dict>
</array>
```

Xcode: Signing & Capabilities > + Sign in with Apple

## Boas PrĂˇticas

1. Sempre tratar `AuthCancelledException` silenciosamente
2. Mostrar mensagem de erro para outras exceĂ§Ăµes
3. Usar `clearError()` apĂłs mostrar erro
4. Apple Sign-In obrigatĂłrio se tiver Google no iOS

